      "description": "<span style=\"color:red\"><strong>Please Note:</strong></span> <em>Due to printing inconsistencies, versions of this card can have either foiling over the entire face of the card or foiling on only the borders of the card, along with foiling color variations for each. You may receive any variation unless specifically noted as a <a href=\"https://help.tcgplayer.com/hc/en-us/articles/360000111067-How-Do-Listings-With-Photos-Work-\">Listing with Photo</a>.</em><br><br>\r\nWhenever Carth the Lion enters the battlefield or a planeswalker you control dies, look at the top seven cards of your library. You may reveal a planeswalker card from among them and put it into your hand. Put the rest on the bottom of your library in a random order.\r\n<br>Planeswalkers' loyalty abilities you activate cost an additional [+1] to activate.",
